    MAX(BK_VAL_RES_FILL_AMOUNT_VAL0) AS "Max Fill Amount"

    dbo.COMPLINE_BK

    timestamp_utc BETWEEN $__timeFrom() AND $__timeTo()

        TYPE_NAME_VAL0 LIKE '%$Search%' OR
        VIN_VAL0 LIKE '%$Search%' OR

    AND BK_CYCLE_RESULT_VAL0 IN ($cycle_result);

    timestamp_utc

    SGMW_GA_PMC.dbo.COMPLINE_BK

    $__timeFilter(timestamp_utc)
    AND (COALESCE('${Search}', '') = '' OR TYPE_NAME_VAL0 = '${Search}')
    AND TYPE_NAME_VAL0 IN ($type_name)
    AND BK_CYCLE_RESULT_VAL0 IN ($cycle_result)
ORDER BY 
    timestamp_utc DESC

SELECT 
    Result_Description,
    COUNT(*) AS Total_Count
FROM (
    SELECT 
        TYPE_NAME_VAL0,
        BK_CYCLE_RESULT_VAL0,
        CASE BK_CYCLE_RESULT_VAL0
            WHEN 1 THEN 'Process OK'
            WHEN 10 THEN 'N.O.K. SYSTEM VACUUM'
            WHEN 11 THEN 'N.O.K. TEST ADAPTER VALVE'
            WHEN 20 THEN 'N.O.K. OVERPRESSURE'
            WHEN 21 THEN 'N.O.K. ADAPTER NOT CLAMPED - VACUUM'
            WHEN 22 THEN 'N.O.K. ADAPTER NOT CLAMPED - POSITION'
            WHEN 23 THEN 'N.O.K. OPEN CAR VALVES'
            WHEN 24 THEN 'N.O.K. PUSH ROD VALVE'
            WHEN 30 THEN 'N.O.K. PRESSURE BUILT-UP'
            WHEN 31 THEN 'N.O.K. PRESSURE LEAK'
            WHEN 32 THEN 'N.O.K. PRESSURE EXHAUST'
            WHEN 33 THEN 'N.O.K. PRESSURE STABILISATION'
            WHEN 34 THEN 'N.O.K. TEST PRESSURE INCREASE IN TANK'
            WHEN 35 THEN 'N.O.K. TANK PRESSURE LIMITS'
            WHEN 40 THEN 'N.O.K. COARSE VACUUM'
            WHEN 41 THEN 'N.O.K. FINE VACUUM'
            WHEN 42 THEN 'N.O.K. VACUUM LEAK TEST'
            WHEN 43 THEN 'N.O.K. POST VACUUM'
            WHEN 44 THEN 'N.O.K. VACUUM TOO QUICK'
            WHEN 45 THEN 'N.O.K. VACUUM STABILISATION'
            WHEN 50 THEN 'N.O.K. FILL PRESSURE'
            WHEN 51 THEN 'N.O.K. FILL AMOUNT'
            WHEN 52 THEN 'N.O.K. FILL TIME'
            WHEN 53 THEN 'N.O.K. FILL ADDI. MEDIUM'
            WHEN 54 THEN 'N.O.K. FILL PRESSURE DECAY'
            WHEN 55 THEN 'N.O.K. TANK PRESSURE'
            WHEN 56 THEN 'N.O.K. FILL TIME AUX. RESERVOIR'
            WHEN 57 THEN 'N.O.K. FILL AMOUNT AUX. RESERVOIR'
            WHEN 58 THEN 'N.O.K. RESIDUAL AIR'
            WHEN 59 THEN 'N.O.K. COUNTER NOT RUNNING'
            WHEN 60 THEN 'N.O.K. COUNTER NOT STANDING STILL'
            WHEN 61 THEN 'N.O.K. LEAK TEST FILL VALVES'
            WHEN 62 THEN 'N.O.K. LEAK TEST CAR VALVES'
            WHEN 63 THEN 'N.O.K. RESET COUNTER'
            WHEN 64 THEN 'N.O.K. RESET COUNTER EXT. RES.'
            WHEN 65 THEN 'N.O.K. FILLING PRESSURE 1'
            WHEN 66 THEN 'N.O.K. FILLING HIGH PRESSURE'
            WHEN 67 THEN 'N.O.K. FILLING PRESSURE 2'
            WHEN 68 THEN 'N.O.K. FILLING DOSING'
            WHEN 69 THEN 'N.O.K. MAX. FILLING VOLUME'
            WHEN 70 THEN 'N.O.K. FILLING PRE STEP'
            WHEN 80 THEN 'N.O.K. ABS FAULT'
            WHEN 81 THEN 'N.O.K. ABS COMMUNICATION'
            WHEN 82 THEN 'N.O.K. ABS SWITCHING NOT STARTED'
            WHEN 83 THEN 'N.O.K. ABS SWITCHING STOPPED IN VACUUM'
            WHEN 84 THEN 'N.O.K. ABS SWITCHING STOPPED IN FILLING'
            WHEN 85 THEN 'N.O.K. ABS SWITCHING STOPPED IN VACUUM (TRW1)'
            WHEN 86 THEN 'N.O.K. ABS SWITCHING STOPPED IN VACUUM (TRW2)'
            WHEN 87 THEN 'N.O.K. CYCLE INTERRUPT FROM VPORT'
            WHEN 88 THEN 'N.O.K. ABS END MISSING'
            WHEN 89 THEN 'N.O.K. ABS FROM VPORT'
            WHEN 90 THEN 'N.O.K. (VPORT) BCM NOT ACTIVATED'
            WHEN 91 THEN 'ERROR WRONG ABS MODULE'
            WHEN 92 THEN 'ERROR CLUTCH NOT IN HOME POSITION'
            WHEN 96 THEN 'N.O.K. WITHOUT FILL'
            WHEN 97 THEN 'N.O.K. COUNTER MODULE'
            WHEN 98 THEN 'N.O.K. USER STOP'
            WHEN 99 THEN 'N.O.K. EQUIPMENT ERROR'
            WHEN 101 THEN 'ERROR SYSTEM VACUUM'
            WHEN 102 THEN 'ERROR ADAPTER VALVE'
            WHEN 103 THEN 'N.O.K. WATER CONTENT'
            WHEN 104 THEN 'ERROR LEAKTEST AT START ON'
            WHEN 105 THEN 'ADD. VACUUM - AERATION'
            WHEN 110 THEN 'ONLY PAG-OIL FILLING SELECTED!'
            WHEN 111 THEN 'PAG-OIL FILLING FINISHED - CONFIRM CLEANING!'
            WHEN 112 THEN 'PAG-OIL FINISHED - PRESS AD. START TO CLEAN ADAPTER!'
            ELSE 'UNKNOWN'
        END AS Result_Description
    FROM dbo.COMPLINE_BK
    WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp_utc)
      AND (COALESCE('${Search}', '') = '' OR TYPE_NAME_VAL0 = '${Search}')
      AND TYPE_NAME_VAL0 IN ($type_name)
      AND BK_CYCLE_RESULT_VAL0 IN ($cycle_result)
) AS Results
GROUP BY Result_Description
ORDER BY Total_Count DESC;

            WHEN 97 THEN 'N.O.K. COUNTER MODULE'
            WHEN 98 THEN 'N.O.K. USER STOP'
            WHEN 99 THEN 'N.O.K. EQUIPMENT ERROR'
            WHEN 101 THEN 'ERROR SYSTEM VACUUM'
            WHEN 102 THEN 'ERROR ADAPTER VALVE'
            WHEN 103 THEN 'N.O.K. WATER CONTENT'
            WHEN 104 THEN 'ERROR LEAKTEST AT START ON'
            WHEN 105 THEN 'ADD. VACUUM - AERATION'
            WHEN 110 THEN 'ONLY PAG-OIL FILLING SELECTED!'
            WHEN 111 THEN 'PAG-OIL FILLING FINISHED - CONFIRM CLEANING!'
            WHEN 112 THEN 'PAG-OIL FINISHED - PRESS AD. START TO CLEAN ADAPTER!'
            ELSE 'UNKNOWN'
        END AS Result_Description
    FROM dbo.COMPLINE_AC
    WHERE $__timeFilter(timestamp_utc)
      AND (COALESCE('${Search}', '') = '' OR AC_TYPE_NAME_VAL0 = '${Search}')
      AND AC_TYPE_NAME_VAL0 IN ($type_name)
      AND AC_CYCLE_RESULT_VAL0 IN ($cycle_result)
) AS Results
GROUP BY Result_Description
ORDER BY Total_Count DESC;
